@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #E8F4F8
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #2B7A78
skinparam ArrowColor #17252A

start

:Ingest **config.yaml**
(Extract Bounding Box & Resolution);

:Coordinate Transformation
**EPSG:4326** (WGS84) → **EPSG:25830** (UTM);

:Spatial Tessellation
(Calculate Sub-region Tile Grid);

repeat :Iterate over Tiles (i, j);
  :WCS **GetCoverage** Request
  (IGN Web Service);
  :Download Tile as 
  TIFF Byte Stream;
repeat while (Are there remaining tiles?) is (Yes)
-> No;

:Merge In-Memory Byte Streams
(Continuous Mosaic via *rasterio*);

:Export Standardized Output
(IDRISI **.doc** & **.img** files);

stop
@enduml